=\"row\" | \"[[Secret Garden (Oh My Girl song)|Secret Garden]]\" {{small|({{lang|ko|\ube44\ubc00\uc815\uc6d0}})}}{{efn|\"Secret Garden (Japanese ver.)\" was released on December 28, 2018 as the second single from ''Oh My Girl Japan Debut Album''.<ref>{{cite web|title=Secret Garden Japanese ver.|url=https://music.line.me/album/mb00000000017aa1c0|website=Line Music|language=ja|accessdate=March 16, 2019}}</ref>}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2018\n| 17 || 17 || \u2014\n| rowspan=\"7\" {{N/A}}\n| ''Secret Garden''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Banana Allergy Monkey\"<br>{{small|({{lang|ko|\ubc14\ub098\ub098 \uc54c\ub7ec\uc9c0 \uc6d0\uc22d\uc774}})}}{{efn|\"Banana Allergy Monkey (Japanese ver.)\" was released on July 25, 2018 as a single from ''Banana Allergy Monkey'', Oh My Girl Banhana's debut Japanese EP.<ref>{{cite web|title=\u30d0\u30ca\u30ca\u304c\u98df\u3079\u308c\u306a\u3044\u30b5\u30eb|url=https://music.line.me/album/mb00000000016b0b64|website=Line Music|language=ja|accessdate=March 16, 2019}}</ref>}}<br>{{small|(As Oh My Girl Banhana)}}\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| ''Banana Allergy Monkey''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Remember Me\" {{small|({{lang|ko|\ubd88\uaf43\ub180\uc774}})}}{{efn|\"Remember Me (Japanese ver.)\" was released on December 21, 2018 as the first single from ''Oh My Girl Japan Debut Album''.<ref>{{cite web|title=\u82b1\u706b(Remember Me) Japanese ver.|url=https://music.line.me/album/mb00000000017a4bc7|website=Line Music|language=ja|accessdate=March 16, 2019}}</ref>}}\n| 36 || 33 || \u2014\n| ''Remember Me''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"The Fifth Season (SSFWL)\"<br>{{small|({{lang|ko|\ub2e4\uc12f \ubc88\uc9f8 \uacc4\uc808}})}}{{efn|\"The Fifth Season (Japanese ver.)\" was released on June 12, 2019 as a single from ''Oh My Girl Japan 2nd Album''.<ref>{{cite web|title=\u4e94\u756a\u76ee\u306e\u5b63\u7bc0 Japanese ver.|url=https://music.line.me/album/mb00000000018e7f55|website=Line Music|language=ja|accessdate=July 9, 2019}}</ref>}}\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2019\n| 26 || 15 || \u2014\n| ''The Fifth Season''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Bungee (Fall in Love)\"{{efn|\"Bungee (Japanese ver.)\" was released on October 30, 2019 as the first single from ''Eternally''.<ref>{{cite web|title=BUNGEE Japanese ver.|url=https://music.line.me/album/mb0000000001a5d40c|website=Line Music|language=ja|accessdate=October 30, 2019}}</ref>}}\n| 50 || 16 || \u2014\n| ''Fall in Love''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Eternally\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| ''Eternally''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Nonstop\"<br>{{small|({{lang|ko|\uc0b4\uc9dd \uc124\ub81c\uc5b4}})}}\n| 2020\n| {{TBA}} || {{TBA}} || \u2014\n| ''Nonstop''\n|-\n| colspan=\"7\" style=\"font-size:8pt;\"| \"\u2014\" denotes releases that did not chart or were not released in that region.\n|}\n\n==Other singles==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|+ List of other charted songs, with selected chart positions and sales figures, showing year released and album name\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:14em;\"|Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:3em;\"|Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"2\" |Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:10em;\"|Sales\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:14em;\"|Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Gaon Digital Chart|KOR]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL |title=Gaon Digital Chart |publisher=[[Gaon Music Chart]]|accessdate=July 10, 2015 |language=ko}}\n*{{cite web |url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=39&hitYear=2019&termGbn=week|title=Destiny|date=September 28, 2019}}\n*{{cite web |url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=45&hitYear=2019&termGbn=week|title=Guerilla|date=November 14, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[K-pop Hot 100|KOR<br>Hot.]]<br><re